## 6. Control System and Firmware
STM32H743ZI (ARM Cortex-M7, 480 MHz) with FreeRTOS. Four priority tiers:
-	**100 kHz** — Phase-locked loop, Eido-Bolt coherence monitoring
-	**20 kHz** — Field-oriented motor control (Clarke/Park transforms, SVM)
-	**10 kHz** — Grid synchronization (SOGI-PLL, configurable for 50/60Hz)
-	**1 Hz** — Thermal management, AWG arbitration, safety interlocks, telemetry
Full firmware source code available in companion repository. Grid interface configurable at compile time for any standard voltage/frequency combination. AWG control integrates into the existing 1 Hz thermal task with no additional interrupt load.
